-- Ramsay Health Care submits joint bid for Generale de Sante
-- By Valentina Za
-- Mon May 12, 2014 02:53AM EDT
-- None



MILAN, May 12 (Reuters) - Australia's Ramsay Health Care <RHC.AX> has presented a joint non-binding offer together with Credit Agricole Assurances and Ramsay Sante to buy 83.43 percent of Generale de Sante <GDSF.PA>, Italian holding company DeA Capital said on Monday.

The offer price of 16.75 euros a share compares with an official closing price on Friday of 15.50 euros each for shares in the French private healthcare group.